Features & Syntax:
    S STR : vary shape: torus, sphere, cylinder, disk
    r N : slice resolution
    M f : major radius
    m f : minor radius
    i f : increment in minor radius between slices
    d N : number of slices to display
    D N : number of slices to save
    f f : fade decay / slice
    a f f : add slice at omega to front
    c N : bucket count
    s : shift slices
    u : update display
    * colormap?
